FBIS4-53653 "dreas099_c_94021" FBIS-EAS-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 North Korea President Kim Il-song Greets Yemeni Leader President Kim Il-song Greets Yemeni Leader SK2105112494 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1106 GMT 21 May 94 SK2105112494 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 21 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea today sent a message of greetings to 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, president of the Presidential Council of the Republic of Yemen, on the occasion of the fourth founding anniversary of the Republic. The message wished him and the Yemeni people success in the efforts to consolidate the unification and stability of the country.
